_sText:
In this small fast paced map, you can choose to play it with the gun game add-on or just a deathmatch with friends or complete strangers.
This map has 4 rooms, 2 secret hallways, a basement for underground fighting, and now a top area for aerial assaults. 
Creates and boxes add extra hiding and assaulting the enemy team. 

Please provide constructive criticism.

New/Changed Features:
-Added access to the top through a large connecting room around the map
-Changed the large doorway a split it into two smaller doorways for less spawn killing

Note- There were many new features with the prev version of the map (The first release online was version 1.0, this is now 1.25)
I'll post the link to download the other versions later, when I get them uploaded.

Install notes-
 1) Unzip gg_unknownfight
 2) Take the maps folder and move it to the Steam Dir/(your username)/counter strike source/cstrike/
 3) Play
